bilingual.source: Cities will be very big and crowded.
bilingual.target: 城市将会非常大且拥挤。

bilingual.source: But I guess it was a little too crowded.
bilingual.target: 但我觉得有点太拥挤了。

bilingual.source: Canada is a lot less crowded than China.
bilingual.target: 加拿大比中国拥挤得少得多。

bilingual.source: The park is the most crowded place on weekends.
bilingual.target: 这个公园是周末最拥挤的地方。

bilingual.source: Well, cities will be more crowded and polluted.
bilingual.target: 嗯，城市将会更加拥挤和污染。

bilingual.source: It is very crowded, and rubbish is also a problem.
bilingual.target: 那里非常拥挤，垃圾也是个问题。

bilingual.source: I do not take the bus to school because it is usually very crowded.
bilingual.target: 我不上学坐公交车，因为通常很拥挤。

bilingual.source: Sometimes trains in Japan are so crowded that railway staff are employed to push passengers inside.
bilingual.target: 有时日本的火车非常拥挤，以至于需要铁路工作人员将乘客推入车厢。

yingyinNormal.en: And that was just the beginning. Headquarters only got more crowded from there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这仅仅是个开始，指挥部从此之后变得越来越拥挤了。

yingyinNormal.en: Weekends are too crowded. So, blow off work, go on a weekday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 周末人太多了。那就不去上班，工作日时去。

yingyinNormal.en: And all the while, I feel I'm standing in the middle of a crowded room screaming at the top of my lungs, and no one even looks up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然而，这时候我觉得自己在人群中高声呐咸却没有人理会，没有人注意。

yingyinNormal.en: But the 67 medals at this year's Games in Rio and 147 at the Paralympics meant that the GB medallists' reception at Buckingham Palace was a crowded and happy event.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是今年，里约奥运收获的67枚奖牌和147枚残奥会奖牌让在白金汉宫举行的奥运健儿欢迎会变的欢愉和热闹。

yingyinNormal.en: Hi, Daddy. There she is, our little girl! Mitchell, do you remember back before we had her how we were so worried that an extra person would make the house feel so crowded?
yingyinNormal.zh: 爸爸。我们的小女孩在这啊，米奇尔，你还记得她来我们家之前我们是怎么担心家里多一个人，是不是会太挤吗？

yingyinNormal.en: But when somebody rips a silent but deadly fart into a crowded room, the brains expectations of reality are smashed by the negative stimulus, making it all seem even more foul.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但若有人不小心在挤满人的地方放了无声的臭屁，大脑接受负面的刺激，让人有味道更臭的错觉了。
